I am a member of team 6420 Fire Island Robotics, and we have a robot design very similar to UMN’s Ri3D design. We would like to source their hand as CAD design but can’t find any way to import the document. We will take the laborous route of re-designing the entire thing, but would also love to work with UMN on this project.
